Vendored copies of the PMLB "first_principles_*" datasets (13 tsv.gz files + metadata.yaml),
fetched 2026-07-10 from https://github.com/EpistasisLab/pmlb (master; data via Git LFS media
endpoint).

License: MIT (PMLB). Copyright (c) 2016 Epistasis Lab at UPenn.

Dataset provenance (per the PMLB metadata):
- 10 datasets (hubble, kepler, newton, ideal_gas, planck, rydberg, leavitt, schechter, bode,
  tully_fisher): EmpiricalBench, from "Interpretable machine learning for science with PySR and
  SymbolicRegression.jl", M. Cranmer, arXiv:2305.01582 (2023).
- 3 datasets (absorption, supernovae_zg, supernovae_zr): Multiview Symbolic Regression,
  E. Russeil et al., GECCO 2024, doi:10.1145/3638529.3654087
  (https://github.com/erusseil/MvSR-analysis).

These files are the build input for the `first-principles` catalog
(tools/build_first_principles.py); the metadata_*.yaml files ground each dataset's provenance,
column semantics, and (where stated) the governing equation.
